msgctxt "84_Hiyori"
msgid "Ugh... I flew off the handle and said I'd never come back, but... Now what?"
msgstr "Ugh... Me salí de control y dije que nunca volvería, pero... ¿Y ahora qué hago?"

msgctxt "96_Hiyori"
msgid "I guess I can go grab my stuff when Dad isn't home, but I can't afford to live alone..."
msgstr "Supongo que puedo ir a buscar mis cosas cuando papá no esté en casa, pero no puedo permitirme vivir sola..."

msgctxt "108_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey. You could try working at a hostess club."
msgstr "Hey. You could try working at a hostess club."

msgctxt "120_Hiyori"
msgid "A hostess club!?"
msgstr "¡¿Un club de hostess?!"

msgctxt "132_Akiyama"
msgid "Sure. Look, I saw you fighting with your father earlier. I understand what you're going through."
msgstr "Sure. Look, I saw you fighting with your father earlier. I understand what you're going through."

msgctxt "144_Hiyori"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "If you promise to work hard, I could even sort out a place for you to live."
msgstr "If you promise to work hard, I could even sort out a place for you to live."

msgctxt "168_Hiyori"
msgid "Really!?"
msgstr "¡¿En serio?!"

msgctxt "180_Akiyama"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr "Claro."

msgctxt "192_Hiyori"
msgid "But I'm not pretty or sexy. I'm hardly the hostess type!"
msgstr "But I'm not pretty or sexy. I'm hardly the hostess type!"

msgctxt "204_Akiyama"
msgid "Don't worry. I'll take care of everything."
msgstr "Don't worry. I'll take care of everything."

msgctxt "216_Hiyori"
msgid "Really? Well... I guess it's worth a try. At least for a little while. Thanks."
msgstr "¿De verdad? Bueno... Supongo que vale la pena intentarlo. Al menos por un tiempo. Gracias."

msgctxt "228_Akiyama"
msgid "Then it's settled. C'mon, let's go to the club."
msgstr "Then it's settled. C'mon, let's go to the club."

